# rtl8188eu
rtl8188eu mac80211 linux driver.

#WARNINNG!!
 This driver has some bugs(may be critical bug).

#TEST DEVICE
 TL-WN725N(0bda:8179)

#HOW TO USE
 if you are using r8188eu module, you should unload r8188eu module.

  rmmod r8188eu
  
 make clean
 
 make
 
 make load
